{"id": 63425, "date": "2025-12-26T04:00:28", "date_gmt": "2025-12-26T12:00:28", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=63425"}, "modified": "2025-11-19T17:16:18", "modified_gmt": "2025-11-20T01:16:18", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-december-26-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/12/26/kingdom-of-days-december-26-2/", "title": {"rendered": "Kingdom of Days: December 26"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>New for 2025:\u00a0</strong>No updates</p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>Bruce drops by the Bottom Line in New York City to catch Patti Smith&#8217;s late show, providing backing vocals for &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/03/16/cover-me-gloria/\">Gloria</a>.&#8221;</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"6749\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1975-1226/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/1975-1226.jpg?fit=314%2C200&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"314,200\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1975-1226\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/1975-1226.jpg?fit=300%2C191&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/1975-1226.jpg?fit=314%2C200&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"wp-image-6749 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/1975-1226-300x191.jpg?resize=758%2C482\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"482\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/1975-1226.jpg?resize=300%2C191&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/1975-1226.jpg?w=314&amp;ssl=1 314w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1995:\u00a0</strong>Bruce announces an extension of his solo acoustic tour in the new year, with select dates in North America before heading overseas.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"31925\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1995-12-2t6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/1995-12-2t6.jpg?fit=794%2C1160&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"794,1160\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1995-12-2t6\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/1995-12-2t6.jpg?fit=205%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/1995-12-2t6.jpg?fit=701%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-31925\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/1995-12-2t6.jpg?resize=758%2C1110&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1110\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2017:\u00a0</strong>Patti Scialfa is sick with the flu and cannot perform, throwing a monkey wrench into the <em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>storyline and set list. Bruce adapts by changing that part of the show to focus on his kids instead of his wife, and accordingly, &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2022/06/19/roll-of-the-dice-long-time-comin/\">Long Time Comin&#8217;</a>&#8221; makes its first appearance in the show, in the spot where &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2020/08/08/roll-of-the-dice-tougher-than-the-rest/\">Tougher Than the Rest</a>&#8221; would normally be. Bruce also swaps out &#8220;<a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/02/06/roll-of-the-dice-brilliant-disguise/\">Brilliant Disguise</a>&#8221; for &#8220;<a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2019/10/17/roll-of-the-dice-the-ghost-of-tom-joad/\">The Ghost of Tom Joad</a>,&#8221; giving added weight to the segment on his social values.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Bruce makes his first guest appearance with Patti Smith, and Patti Scialfa misses her first Broadway show with Bruce. </p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 6062, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}}, "categories": [2], "tags": [630, 115, 1071, 273], "class_list": ["post-63425", "post", "type-post", "status-publish", "format-standard", "has-post-thumbnail", "hentry", "cat